1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,500
I'm the transfer student, Shinji Ikari. Nice to meet you.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,500
That guy is the Eva pilot? A normal kid like him?

3
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,500
Toji, your sister got hurt in that battle, right? It's his fault.

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,500
Why are you hitting me? It's not like I wanted to pilot the Eva.

5
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:37,000
Emergency situation. The Fourth Angel is approaching from the Hakone Mountain area. All personnel, assume Level One battle stations.

6
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:44,000
Shinji Ikari, report to NERV headquarters immediately. Repeat, report immediately.

7
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:51,000
Eva Unit-01, commencing activation sequence. The pilot's mental state is unstable.

8
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:58,000
It doesn't matter. Send him out. There is no other means to defeat the Angel.

9
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:05,000
Distance to target, 1200 meters. Now within firing range.

10
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:12,000
Suppress it with the pallet rifle. Neutralizing the AT Field is top priority.

11
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:19,000
Unable to neutralize the AT Field! Insufficient power output!

12
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:26,000
The power cable has been severed! Switching to internal battery. Four minutes and thirty-two seconds until operational limit.

13
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:33,000
Ikari, stay calm. You can do this. Focus.

14
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:40,000
Use the progressive knife! Force it into close combat!

15
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:47,000
Angel core confirmed. Destroying that red sphere should defeat it.

16
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:54,000
Thirty seconds until operational limit. Hurry, Ikari!

17
00:01:57,500 --> 00:02:01,000
Angel, activity ceased. Core destruction confirmed. Operation complete.

18
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:08,000
That was incredible, Ikari. You really defeated the Angel.

19
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:15,000
Nobody ever calls. Even if I weren't here, nobody would care.

20
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:22,000
Ikari, you're always alone, aren't you? You look kind of lonely.
